text.tspan: Assertive school administrator with years of experience supporting schools to improve continuously. Set
standards and encouraged students to make standards achievable. Increased test scores by 30%.
Handled disciplinary referrals with a calm, logical approach to student behavior.
Met with parents of prospective students to discuss student needs and school offerings.
Attended annual meetings with special education and 504 students to represent needs of the school
Supported teachers in learning and applying new skills through meaningful professional development.
Supervised, assessed and mentored teachers and paraprofessionals.
Proposed and executed budget of $70,000 per school year.
Supported human resources operations, including hiring, training, disciplinary action and termination in
compliance with legal guidelines and requirements.
Performed classroom evaluations to assess teacher strategies and effectiveness.
